data.description: Well maintained and move-in ready 3 bedroom/1 bathroom RANCH located in a neighborhood setting. Features a sunny and bright living room with a wood burning fireplace, bay window, recessed lighting, crown molding and built-in book shelves. The bedrooms have double closets and new Berber wall-to-wall carpet with extra cushion padding. The kitchen/dining room area with a bay window, leads out to a beautiful patio, gazebo, and outdoor firepit overlooking a mix of annual and perennial flowers. Updates include new exterior doors, new garage door, and a new sump pump. Plenty of storage space in the full walkout basement, and in the backyard shed. Close to shopping, restaurants, and highways, this home is a MUST SEE!
